title: in 35 minutes our Darius did 10.3K damage.
body: I, on Rakan, did 9.6K. Admittedly he was in a hard matchup against a Teemo, but all he needed to do was sit at his turret and farm because Nunu literally spent the entire game bot because without him their bot would get 2 v 2'd all day (Sona even squishier than usual as she went 0 resists).
